    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat</b> The berserker uses the knockdown rage power on enemies who are heavily armored or wield heavy weapons.<br/><b>Base Statistics</b> When she\u2019s not raging, the berserker\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>21, touch 12, flat-footed 19; <b>hp </b>54; <b>Fort </b>+9, <b>Will </b>+2; <b>Melee </b>mwk morningstar +10 (1d8+4), bite +7 (1d6+3) or claw +9 (1d4+3), bite +7 (1d6+2); <b>Str </b>18, <b>Con </b>15; <b>CMB </b>+9; <b>Skills </b>Swim +19."
        },
        {
